snippet.textDisplay: I like how this song is essentially a direct contrast to their last album Neotheater which I believe is all about being reluctant to grow up and wanting to stay in blissful ignorance. Especially for their song “Next Up Forever” where they are reluctant to even start to grow up or in a more real since release the album. Not wanting to ever hit their peak and have fun. This is a song about accepting growth and going out with a bang. Passing their peak and accepting that it’s time to take the bow or grow up and face the future. Or I’m reading to much into this and I’m just a weirdo. Anyway let me know what u think! :)
